[30;1m56 | [0m[35mUsage[0m
[30;1m57 | [0m[35m-----[0m

[30;1m54 | [0m[35mHowever, if you have a large library, then you might prefer to ship[0m

[30;1m19 | [0m[35m- Options should be environment variables (these lend themselves better to YML config files). They s[0m
[30;1m20 | [0m[35m- Options should be generalised to all platforms. If platform-specific options are required, they sh[0m
